independent_work.et:
Throughout the course students are expected to:
- read all compulsory readings;
- submit questions and reflections for seminars;
- attend at least 50% of lectures and seminars;
- follow announcements by the lecturer;
- discuss invented essay topics with the lecturer;
- accomplish all compulsory assignments (2 argumentative essays and a group presentation)

Independent works:
1) reading texts and sending questions and reflections for seminar discussions,
2) writing and submitting 2 argumentative essays, and
3) preparing a group presentation for the final discussion.

Guidelines for completing the assignments will be added to Moodle and will be explained during the first meeting.
